{"word":"G4372 - πρόσφατος - prósphatos - pros'-fat-os - New","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρόσφατος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prósphatos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros'-fat-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">New</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"புதிய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. lately slaughtered, freshly killed"},{"paragraph":"2. recently or very lately made, new"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4969 - σφάζω - spházō - sfad'-zo/4969\">G4969</a>; <i>previously</i> (<i>recently</i>) <i>slain</i> (<i>fresh</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>lately made:</i> - new.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4372/4372\">G4372</a>, <a href=\"#/G4373/4373\">G4373</a>"}]}